I, Trevor Drayton, have developed the Interval Timer app as a free-to-use app. This SERVICE is provided by me at no cost and is intended for use as is.

This page is used to inform users regarding my policies with the absence of the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information.

**1. No Collection of Personal Information**

Interval Timer does not collect any Personal Information. 

**2. No Use or Disclosure of Personal Information**

As Interval Timer does not collect any Personal Information, it does not use or disclose your information.

**3. No Third-Party Access**

No third parties have access to user information, as Interval Timer does not collect any user data.

**4. Security**

Despite the fact that Interval Timer does not collect Personal Information, I am committed to ensuring the security and protection of any data the app interacts with.

**5. Changes to This Privacy Policy**

I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

This policy is effective as of July 8, 2023.

**6. Contact Us**

If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at trevorpdrayton@gmail.com.
